stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Validating: User submits form
    Validating --> Idle: Validation errors
    Validating --> Filtering: Valid preferences
    Filtering --> EmptyState: Zero candidates
    Filtering --> Loading: Has candidates
    Loading --> Success: LLM + parse OK
    Loading --> Fallback: LLM error
    Success --> Idle: User changes preferences
    Fallback --> Idle: User changes preferences
    EmptyState --> Idle: User changes preferences